<!--
  HandyAi — three-bubble conversation mark.
  Replaces the Gemini-like AutoAwesome sparkle as the app's brand icon.
  Three overlapping rounded speech bubbles evoke a multi-turn conversation:
    - Back bubble (top-left, largest)
    - Middle bubble (right, medium)
    - Front bubble (bottom-right, small, with tail)
  Drawn with a single fill so Compose's Icon tint recolors the whole mark.
-->
